text: Rosa Maria Carrasco i Azemar (2 July 1936 - 6 August 2018) was a Spanish politician. She was born in Barcelona. She was known as one of the founders of the Democrats of Catalonia party.Muere Rosa M. Carrasco, hija de un histórico de UDC y fundadora de Demòcrates Carrasco Azemar died in Barcelona from a stroke on 6 August 2018, aged 82.Muere a los 82 años Rosa Maria Carrasco, hija de Carrasco i Formiguera ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Deaths from stroke Category:Politicians from Barcelona
